Jeremia onyiso Baruk wach moa kuom Nyasaye


1  

E higa mar ang’wen mar loch Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, Baruk wuod Neria nondiko weche mane Jeremia owachone. Bang’e Jeremia janabi nonyiso 
2  Baruk niya, “Weche ma Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel owacho kuomi e magi: 
3  ‘In iwacho ni tinde iol, nikech Ruoth Nyasaye osemedoni mana kuyo kuom thagruok ma in go. Bende iwacho ni iseywak miol, to ok iseyudo kue ngang’.’ 
4  Kuom mano, Ruoth Nyasaye owacho mondo anyisi kama: ‘Abiro muko gik moko duto ma asegero, kendo pudho gik ma asepidho. Abiro timo kamano e piny ngima. 
5  Idwaro mondo iyud gik ma dongo dongo, to onego iwe dwarogi, nimar abiro kelo masira ni ji duto e piny. In to, initony kamoro amora midhiye, to ngimani kende ema niresi.’ ”

